Drusilla Wills https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Drusilla_Wills 0 Drusilla Wills (1884-1951) was a British stage and film actress. After making her stage debut in 1902, she played character roles in many films, including as a jury member in Alfred Hitchcock's Murder! (1930).
